: {"text": "近日，工信部印发《关于加强智能网联汽车生产企业及产品准入管理的意见》。《意见》要求，企业实施在线升级活动前，应当确保汽车产品符合国家法律法规、技术标准及技术规范等相关要求并向工业和信息化部备案，涉及安全、节能、环保、防盗等技术参数变更的应提前向工业和信息化部申报，保证汽车产品生产一致性。未经审批，不得通过在线等软件升级方式新增或更新汽车自动驾驶功能。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2bb8245e052b20d7a4e6c970801f068_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "112 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479186205"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5sGUi9/KxdYuEAMaCDY4NzY3MDc1IL200ogGMAI4hAFAIXIJNDc5MTg2MjA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1628798542.701479", "card_id": "Q_456543158", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你的藏书架上，至今最得意的藏书是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1885cff39b336fbc14cced4e9e988618_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/456543158"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5sGUi9/KxdYuEAMaCDYzNzMzOTY0IJPdlYQGMAI4vwJAInIJNDU2NTQzMTU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1628798542.701776", "card_id": "Q_478905840", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "该如何正确地读一本书？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "读书很重要，读什么书也很重要，但感觉怎样读书，怎样吸收内化好像更重要。 以前读书总是跟着作者走，后来发现书其实也只是作者见解的一种传达，故有深浅、正误之分，于是看书就开始有意识地挑选、思辨，但看着看着就发现自己看书的目的性在弱化，整理笔记、写书评渐渐有些无从下手。是我的方法有问题吗？怎样解决呢？求教"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-147779e9a3428f27b0dbb682f3a6a219_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/478905840"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5sGUi9/KxdYuEAMaCDY4NzA0NzYwINzxzIgGMAA4mAFAI3IJNDc4OTA1ODQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": 